A flashmob saw young dancers from Limpopo take to the floor at Savannah Mall, where they danced to  local pop and hip hop, reports Bosveld Review.

READ MORE: Steve Hofmeyr’s traffic flashmob video released
The dance display was in honour of Nelson Mandela, and ensured that shoppers left the mall with a smile.

